{"tid":2188784,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對住個後父真係好矛盾","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T07:39:11.000Z","uid":77235,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"df9929d663640fd6a1978ffd37e9c9b075df1e70","tid":2188784,"uid":77235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"雖然相處左十幾年 但都無老豆既感覺<br />\n無果種為人子女對父母任性果種感覺<br />\n咁多年一路都好以禮相待 唔敢要求乜野<br />\n細個唔敢問佢拎零用 唔敢問佢拎資源補習 去興趣班 唔敢發佢脾氣<br />\n出黎做野佢又唔要我家用<br />\n依家佢開始老 明明佢可以退休 我都成日叫佢早啲休息<br />\n但佢又好勤力去搵生意 話想賺多啲比我<br />\n一方面 錢梗係越多越好 難得佢咁錫我<br />\n但另一方面 又覺得唔係咁好意思 大家非親非故 要你為我咁辛苦 但我比唔到咩回報你"},{"pid":"a4f3e236d099d165cfed4ef384dd1da6a8fd923e","tid":2188784,"uid":136797,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"以身相許囉臭雞"},{"pid":"66dad55dea32c3af3f104827c4b2652ae0127b24","tid":2188784,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"唔通...係愛呀..."},{"pid":"d61197cf612feb20af3553ac9664e1d07f832fa6","tid":2188784,"uid":179649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"愛屋及烏姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔排除佢都愛你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fab64dfb2909dcbee8add71cb9d5fc706f10e02","tid":2188784,"uid":39488,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"你有俾佢屌架"},{"pid":"2ba19ff07853031cd814830aca232f4aa1bddb04","tid":2188784,"uid":118311,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"佢心底係愛你既"},{"pid":"79ebd3073d4e99b0675a57c714d6010bb55210a6","tid":2188784,"uid":343964,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"樓上啲留言jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d515c00cef5ac43f800baf53fda22aca77e6b2